## Vite config confirmed

```js
base: '/demos/audio-software-engineer-needed-for/',
```
`import.meta.env.BASE_URL` will correctly be `/demos/audio-software-engineer-needed-for/` in production. Audio URLs will be `/demos/audio-software-engineer-needed-for/audio/<slug>/<file>.mp3` — correct for GH Pages.

Audio files in `demo-src/public/audio/` are served verbatim by Vite (not bundled). Vite may print large-file warnings but these are not build errors.

